"title": "6627: conversion, nature of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "6627",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>True repentance results in a turning from sin and an inner renewal which can only be brought about by God, who draws people to himself and who, through Jesus Christ, gives forgiveness and new life.</p>\n<h2>Conversion as turning to God</h2>\n<h3>Turning back to God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:30-Deut4:31\">DEU 4:30–4:31</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:16-Luke1:17\">LUK 1:16–1:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut30:2-Deut30:3\">DEU 30:2–30:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut30:10\">DEU 30:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:32\">LUK 22:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:19-Jas5:20\">JAS 5:19–5:20</a></p>\n<h3>Turning from idolatry</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:15\">ACT 14:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam7:3\">1SA 7:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer3:12-Jer3:13\">JER 3:12–3:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer4:1-Jer4:2\">JER 4:1–4:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess1:9-1Thess1:10\">1TH 1:9–1:10</a></p>\n<h3>Turning from sinful ways</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:13-2Kgs17:14\">2KI 17:13–17:14</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa55:6-Isa55:7\">ISA 55:6–55:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs13:11\">2KI 13:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs14:24\">2KI 14:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs15:9\">2KI 15:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer18:11\">JER 18:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer25:5\">JER 25:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek18:23\">EZK 18:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan9:13\">DAN 9:13</a></p>\n<h2>Conversion as a turning away from unbelief to faith</h2>\n<h3>It is linked to repentance</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:19\">ACT 3:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek14:6\">EZK 14:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek18:30\">EZK 18:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:20\">ACT 26:20</a></p>\n<h3>It is linked to coming to faith</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:21\">ACT 11:21</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Conversion brings new life</h2>\n<h3>It results in a transformed life</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:17\">2CO 5:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:2\">ROM 12:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor3:18\">2CO 3:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:14-Gal6:15\">GAL 6:14–6:15</a></p>\n<h3>It is symbolised in baptism</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:3-Rom6:4\">ROM 6:3–6:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:12\">COL 2:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:1-Col3:3\">COL 3:1–3:3</a></p>\n<h3>It demands a new lifestyle</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos12:6\">HOS 12:6</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:3-Matt18:4\">MAT 18:3–18:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:22-Gal5:24\">GAL 5:22–5:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:1\">EPH 4:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:8-Eph5:11\">EPH 5:8–5:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:11-1Pet2:12\">1PE 2:11–2:12</a></p>\n<h2>Conversion brings a new relationship with God</h2>\n<h3>It brings a new status</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:7\">GAL 4:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:26-Gal3:29\">GAL 3:26–3:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:1\">1JN 3:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:9-1Pet2:10\">1PE 2:9–2:10</a></p>\n<h3>It brings a new understanding</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor3:15-2Cor3:16\">2CO 3:15–3:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:34\">JER 31:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb8:11\">HEB 8:11</a></p>\n<h2>Conversion is a work of God</h2>\n<h3>God turns people to himself</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer24:7\">JER 24:7</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam5:21\">LAM 5:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:58\">1KI 8:58</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:18\">JER 31:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek36:26-Ezek36:27\">EZK 36:26–36:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:44\">JHN 6:44</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:16\">JHN 15:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:12-Eph2:13\">EPH 2:12–2:13</a></p>\n<h3>God gives new birth</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:17-Jas1:18\">JAS 1:17–1:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:3-John3:6\">JHN 3:3–3:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:4-Titus3:5\">TIT 3:4–3:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:23\">1PE 1:23</a></p>",
